    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457913>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Oswaldella occulta sp. nov. UnfOrked hydrOcladial inTernOdes, wiTh hydrOTheca, mesial superiOr nemaTOphOre and mesial inferiOr nemaTOTheca. Scale bar: 250 µm." ;
